Popular artist, Davido Adeleke who recently welcomed a bundle of joy with his fiancee, Chioma has taken to his Instagram page to reveal his excitement as his son officially becomes a US citizen. Ifeanyi Adeleke who was born in London now holds dual citizenship of Nigeria and the United States of America The proud and ecstatic father could not contain his joy as he shared the news on his insta story. The singer who also bears dual citizenship was born in Atlanta, Georgia, United States. Source